title: I Don't Like Hugs
description:
Welcome to Bob The Drag Queen & Monét X Change's new podcast, Sibling Rivalry. In this episode Bob & Monét discuss celebrity etiquette, Jessie J & why Monét won't stop eating during the podcast. Follow: @bobthedragqueen @monetxchange Presented by: The Only Productions Do you love sibling rivalry?
